    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/01069796d76795d075aa10027c60a61c.webp?t=1729181401\" width=610 height=26 /></span><br><br>《塔尼蚀：神之堕落》将暗黑幻想题材、绕梁三日的精美配乐、极具挑战的魂系2D动作RPG玩法、以及语焉不详的叙事结合为一体。富有创新的爽快战斗系统、类型和风格多样的装备与能力、高度精细的像素美术、以及富有压迫感的Boss战–––所有这些结合起来，令《塔尼蚀：神之堕落》的旅程沉浸感十足，难以忘怀。<br><br><strong>一场史诗英雄冒险：</strong>15种风格迥异的关卡场景、14场惊险的Boss战、以及诸多秘密和支线任务，都在这个流程长达20+小时的动作RPG中等待你的探索。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/a2494efb9db9fd26210586aa67f99936.poster.avif?t=1729181401\" width=698 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/a2494efb9db9fd26210586aa67f99936.webm?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/a2494efb9db9fd26210586aa67f99936.mp4?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>高风险高回报的爽快战斗：</strong>独特的“能量泉涌”系统，允许玩家通过连击获得持续的精力和魔力回复加成，鼓励不断进攻，愈战愈勇。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/53741ae6e11f0fe5dac651c702a08fc5.poster.avif?t=1729181401\" width=692 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/53741ae6e11f0fe5dac651c702a08fc5.webm?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/53741ae6e11f0fe5dac651c702a08fc5.mp4?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>极具压迫感的Boss战：</strong>与邪恶正面对决！和堕落圣徒、古代战争机械、被侵蚀的生物和破坏力十足的神祇对峙，在凶险的多阶段Boss战中将你的战斗技术与意志推向极限。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/08bf28f34fa652eb150f7bc340daf32d.poster.avif?t=1729181401\" width=698 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/08bf28f34fa652eb150f7bc340daf32d.webm?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/08bf28f34fa652eb150f7bc340daf32d.mp4?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>赢得强大的新能力：</strong>击败Boss获取圣物，选择称心如意的终极攻防技能组合，并借助它们扭转战斗局势！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/e87a9b948f476475fb838fc62e95d661.poster.avif?t=1729181401\" width=652 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/e87a9b948f476475fb838fc62e95d661.webm?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/e87a9b948f476475fb838fc62e95d661.mp4?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>开发独一无二的角色构建：</strong>搜寻独特的武器、盔甲套装、魔法技能、圣物等等。鼓励玩家尝试不同的组合，打造出最适合自己游玩风格和喜爱的独特角色构建。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/64193d4f4fcba42694f868a8f78fed93.poster.avif?t=1729181401\" width=698 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/64193d4f4fcba42694f868a8f78fed93.webm?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/64193d4f4fcba42694f868a8f78fed93.mp4?t=1729181401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428710/extras/9a7daca8bb75bd34a64aa667c81b71b3.webp?t=1729181401\" width=610 height=26 /></span>",
